    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to become roadworthy again. The engine currently struggles to start and has a noticeable knock, while the transmission slips between gears. Cosmetically, the body shows extensive rust, several large dents, and the paint is peeling across most surfaces. Inside, the upholstery is heavily torn and the electronics are largely non-functional. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts, and it will likely need to be towed from its current location.",
      "price": 8500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
