    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine gliding through the golden hour, the engine humming a low, confident melody that feels less like machinery and more like a heartbeat. This is a preserved masterpiece, finished in a coat of paint that captures the moonlight and an interior that breathes with the scent of hand-tailored leather and quiet ambition. Every curve tells a story of unparalleled elegance, standing as a silent testament to an era when craftsmanship was a philosophy. It is not merely a vehicle, but a passport to a more refined world, waiting for a driver who understands that some legends never fade.",
      "price": 48900.0,
