    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a pinnacle-spec E92 M3, a true collector-grade example of the high-revving S65 V8 era. This vehicle has been maintained with an open-wallet policy, featuring a proactive rod bearing replacement using treated shells and ARP bolts to ensure bottom-end longevity. The double-VANOS system has been meticulously timed and tested for zero deviation, providing a linear power band all the way to the 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis is tightened with upgraded subframe bushings to eliminate deflection, and the DCT firmware has been flashed to GTS specs for lightning-fast actuation. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, reflecting a factory-fresh luster without the typical road rash. This is a turn-key, mechanically synchronized machine for the discerning driver who demands zero parasitic power loss and absolute structural rigidity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
